  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Added</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Add realtime to the service scale page</li>\n<li>Add experimental feature to allow project links through network policy</li>\n<li>Add cluster name as an environment variable \"LCP_PROJECT_CLUSTER\" to deployed containers</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Changed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Update Service Popover to include CPU, Memory, and Transfer usage</li>\n<li>Changes tooltip message when hovering a service from a build to include the version that was built</li>\n<li>Hides the \"more\" button in case the user has no actions to perform when paginating items</li>\n<li>Update permissions to allow Guests to download logs</li>\n<li>Retrieve only unread alerts to mark them as read</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Fixed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix decimal CPU values displayed improperly on service tooltip</li>\n<li>Fix feedback when restore is in progress or finished</li>\n<li>Fix endpoints tooltip rendering wrong when navigating from overview page</li>\n<li>Fix number of instances wrongly shown on the services page</li>\n<li>Fix backup restore card showing the current user instead of the restore author</li>\n<li>Fix discrepancies in activities list</li>\n<li>Fix returning the latest build when doing API requests</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Security</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Add a blacklist of vulnerable service versions and block builds that contain them</li>\n</ul>"
      },
